{"tid":1562024,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"［痛苦］有冇巴絲分享吓手足口病","createTime":"2019-09-12T00:23:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T00:54:15.000Z","uid":48980,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"b66195a4e6eab32fe3c57193ba89054fb082f67a","tid":1562024,"uid":48980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T00:23:56.000Z","msg":"小弟不幸 中左手足口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第一日發燒同有啲喉嚨痛 睇左醫生退左以為冇野<br />\n之後第二日就發現瀨野啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n照一照個口入面 哇屌！ 好撚多粒飛滋生左係喉嚨<br />\n之後晏啲隻手有細粒水泡咁出左黎<br />\n屌！中左手足口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家係房隔離緊 冇番工 喉嚨痛到仆街食唔到飲唔到野 好似比刀界一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇巴絲試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好絕望"},{"pid":"9bdba3aa4973215c48fb5c83ea32606724ff0710","tid":1562024,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T00:24:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"ec7a510055bece1ce74640477273c6843a99ef45","tid":1562024,"uid":76702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T00:24:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e415bb044cfded632a2f44db3e1005a2add86eae","tid":1562024,"uid":158585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T00:25:53.000Z","msg":"定係性病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb7c401f4e3d3aa2fb180d5dd5ea138f504c77ef","tid":1562024,"uid":195223,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T00:26:58.000Z","msg":"飲水都痛到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6a52c88f20d42b37affd15a63d696052bae860c","tid":1562024,"uid":10954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T00:28:37.000Z","msg":"唔係食唔到野咁簡單<br />\n係連吞口水飲水都痛到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n起碼抖返個幾星期先好返"},{"pid":"89ca6f4fdda1301cdb9ceb15176bc9ad7818340b","tid":1562024,"uid":48980,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fb7c401f4e3d3aa2fb180d5dd5ea138f504c77ef","tid":1562024,"uid":195223,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T00:26:58.000Z","msg":"飲水都痛到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T00:28:53.000Z","msg":"每一啖都好似比刀界一下咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c66d70bb8894e1bf375850c805af0cf31dcb4de","tid":1562024,"uid":66945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T00:29:15.000Z","msg":"我啲紅點冇咩特別，只係手指嗰啲摸落去唔舒服<br />\n我發燒嗰日未知係手足口，仲同男友share一碗麵食，最後佢都中招<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9243516470293e9494efc0136d7c0116848ee2f4","tid":1562024,"uid":48980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c66d70bb8894e1bf375850c805af0cf31dcb4de","tid":1562024,"uid":66945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T00:29:15.000Z","msg":"我啲紅點冇咩特別，只係手指嗰啲摸落去唔舒服<br />\n我發燒嗰日未知係手足口，仲同男友share一碗麵食，最後佢都中招<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T00:31:10.000Z","msg":"比死更難受而家<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec1d3cf438d97185e5c0c4c4a788bcba1ffb3ace","tid":1562024,"uid":67315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T00:32:14.000Z","msg":"分享手足口病<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46b102c7c0b190affa2e0d8dc35aed4beecff611","tid":1562024,"uid":48980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T00:38:53.000Z","msg":"想食野都食唔到 係房隔離好無聊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9ac04dc15dc4613851e01bc066bbf71cdb587c0","tid":1562024,"uid":108756,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T00:41:45.000Z","msg":"有<br />\n中過一次 仆街第一日都估撚到唔係普通野 個人起身個陣攰撚到仆街 係去到感覺到真係唔返得工個隻請左假 諗住訓到中午起身睇醫生<br />\n第一日個醫生仲話我係扁桃腺發炎 開抗生素又剩<br />\n第三日再睇多次 因為啲手腳出埋紅點 醫生先話原來手足口<br />\n開多五日定一星期藥 加直頭俾五日病假 每日完全係訓醒食啲啲野食藥又訓返 每日二十四小時唔知有無醒過四小時<br />\n咁大個人未試過咁樣病法<br />\n不過個人唔知係咪有被虐 每次生菲之都鍾意整痛佢 好享受個種痛<br />\n所以每日都逼自己當無事咁吞口水 但食野真係唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過上網睇好似過中一次得抗體"},{"pid":"938254128a4e9c74db3f83639944d80e825533fd","tid":1562024,"uid":279810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T00:44:36.000Z","msg":"生飛滋飲鹽水冇咁痛, 唔知咩原理, <br />\n但次次都 work"},{"pid":"a8a53ef79cfc8c4c051f72752ab8f75eb0959f9c","tid":1562024,"uid":294635,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T00:49:59.000Z","msg":"好返手腳甩皮先係地獄<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65c784176033cc401b7943af547a98688f5180f0","tid":1562024,"uid":48980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T01:17:11.000Z","msg":"好似睇次醫生穩陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac74aa266